node.text:
Is your dream suit so unique that only really you could design it? If so, we have a surprise for you! Introducing our D.I.Y. Swimsuit Kit. It comes with everything you need to sew your perfect suit from scratch. Sound crazy? It's easier than you'd think! Link in bio to find out more! 

#jolyn #diy #swimsuit

node.text:
“Our whole life doesn’t revolve around our disability,” she said. “I drive such a cute car and I get iced coffee every day. I live a really good life, if I’m going to be honest.”⁠
- Haven Shepard ⁠
⁠
Meet our JOPRO Haven, She is a double amputee after losing her lower legs at 14 months old by a bomb. In spite of this she is one of the rising stars in the U.S. Para swimming program AND one for the most positive individuals around! #chooseJOY ⁠
⁠
#jolyn #thenandnow #lookatmenow

node.text:
Meet Hallie, university senior  and swim-national athlete at USC⁠
Hallie is majoring in human biology and minoring in healthcare studies. ⁠
⁠
So far Hallie has been invited to 3 NCAAs, named an honorary all American and qualified for my second Olympic trials. 🤭⁠
Although her past season was not the fastest in the water, it’s the year she feels the most proud of because she had the opportunity to join an inspirational group of women who helped her fall back in L💙VE with swimming. ⁠
⁠
This summer Hallie will be working a research internship in LA while training for US Open at the end of the summer and starting to prep for year two as a TROJAN 🤩
